&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://scraps.hecticjeff.net/backbonejs-tips-lessons-from-the-trenches&quot;&gt;Backbone.js Tips : Lessons from the trenches&lt;/a&gt;
